that they should replace the verification system.

00:10:25.870 --> 00:10:26.850
Yeah.

00:10:26.860 --> 00:10:28.910
You know, you have to crawl before you go, Dave

00:10:28.910 --> 00:10:31.340
, you know, a real problem that was being solved in

00:10:31.340 --> 00:10:35.070
real time right away and clearly the right thing to do.

00:10:35.110 --> 00:10:36.860
But I think this is a good migration.

00:10:36.870 --> 00:10:37.850
Yeah.

00:10:37.870 --> 00:10:38.860
Absolutely.

00:10:38.870 --> 00:10:39.860
Fantastic.

00:10:39.870 --> 00:10:40.850
There was a question over here.

00:10:40.860 --> 00:10:41.850
Oh.

00:10:41.860 --> 00:10:42.850
