Well, it's, I mean, it, I mean

00:11:06.600 --> 00:11:09.200
, yeah, it is, it's in there.

00:11:09.200 --> 00:11:10.190
I mean.

00:11:10.200 --> 00:11:12.280
So there's, there's, you know, like you

00:11:12.290 --> 00:11:15.200
talked, so a lot of content made it onto the floor

